Usage:  usermgmt --help
        usermgmt <command> <sub_command> [<sub_command_options>]

Manage the users and groups.

<command> <sub_command> must be one of the following pairs:
        group add
        group modify
        group delete
        group list
        user add
        user modify
        user delete
        user list

<sub_command_options>   call "usermgmt <command> <sub_command> --help" 
                        for more details.
